Edi Patterson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edi_Patterson 0 Edi Patterson is an American comedy actress, best known for playing Veronica in Partners, and as Ms. Abbott in Vice Principals from 2016 to 2017. Edi Patterson was born in Texas City, Texas, United States, to her mother, who was a teacher, and her father, who was a plumber. She graduated from the Southwest Texas State, and became an improv performer in Austin, Texas. Her career to date includes regular roles in many TV series including The Underground in 2006, Partners in 2014, Black-ish in 2015, Vice Principals (2016–2017), and We Bare Bears (voice only) (2015–2018).
